<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New User Registration - Whiskarz Pet-Sitting</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #2C3E50; 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 650px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(26, 42, 108, 0.1);
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A2A6C 0%, #0F3460 100%);
            color: white; 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
        }
        .header h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 400;
            opacity: 0.95;
            color: white;
        }
        .logo-badge {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .content { 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .user-info-box {
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
            border: 2px solid #00AEEF;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .user-info-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1A2A6C;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .user-info-box ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 15px 0 0 0;
        }
        .user-info-box li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 12px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 3px solid #00AEEF;
            color: #2C3E50;
        }
        .user-info-box li strong {
            color: #1A2A6C;
            font-weight: 600;
            min-width: 120px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .action-box {
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #1A2A6C;
        }
        .action-box p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            color: #2C3E50;
        }
        .action-box strong {
            color: #1A2A6C;
        }
        .footer { 
            background-color: #2C3E50;
            padding: 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #F5F7FA;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            color: #F5F7FA;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #00AEEF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #00AEEF;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo-badge">üîî</div>
                <h1>Whiskarz Pet-Sitting System</h1>
                <h2>New User Registration</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #2C3E50;">Hello <strong style="color: #1A2A6C;">Admin</strong>,</p>
                
                <p style="color: #2C3E50;">A new user has registered and is pending approval:</p>

                <div class="status-badge">
                    ‚è≥ PENDING APPROVAL
                </div>

                <div class="user-info-box">
                    <h3>üë§ User Information</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Name:</strong> 
                            <span>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Email:</strong> 
                            <span>{{email}}</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Role:</strong> 
                            <span>{{role}}</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Registration Date:</strong> 
                            <span>{{registrationDate}}</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="action-box">
                    <p><strong>‚ö° Action Required:</strong></p>
                    <p>Please review and approve or reject this user in the admin panel.</p>
                </div>

                <hr class="divider">

                <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #2C3E50;">
                    <strong>Best regards,</strong><br>
                    <span style="color: #1A2A6C; font-weight: 700;">Whiskarz Pet-Sitting System</span> üêæ
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #00AEEF; margin-bottom: 15px;">üêæ Whiskarz Pet-Sitting üêæ</p>
                <p><strong>üìß Admin & Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:admin@whiskarz.com">admin@whiskarz.com</a></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; opacity: 0.8;">&copy; 2025 Whiskarz Pet-Sitting. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
